comment: Journalists will, at some point, realise that our summer is the Southern hemisphere's winter, and vice versa, and that winter conditions increase flu cases in general populations - and why the Southern hemisphere has their flu season during our summer.
@katearthsis @TheAngelofWrath it hasn't been determined that warmer temps decrease spread has it?
@Kane9015 @TheAngelofWrath It's still within the coronavirus family. So, it's still susceptible to the same things to an extent as the other coronaviruses
